/* ==========================================================================
   TQuant Lab - Extra Stylesheet
   Organized & Cleaned Up Version
   ==========================================================================
   
   Table of Contents:
   1. CSS Variables
   2. Layout & Grid
   3. Sidebar Styles
   4. Light Theme
   5. Dark Theme
   6. Typography
   7. Header & Footer
   8. Search Box
   9. Code Blocks
   10. Admonitions
   11. Tables
   12. Links
   13. Mermaid Diagrams
   14. UI Components (Buttons, Toggles)
